{"tid":1699652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紀念周同學 認識科大口號","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T06:25:08.000Z","uid":300761,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4084b4c601a1da606034c2a51dde3ecf888df6d8","tid":1699652,"uid":300761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"話說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />科大門口有條路 上面寫咗句口號 可以話係科大嘅革命精神<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望在於人民 改變始於抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然冇咩外人識呢個口號 雖然科大多港豬 但因為今次周同學嘅事件 相信都會有好多科大人走出嚟<br />\n<br />\n如果發夢聽到有人叫呢句口號 大家可唔可以<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">跟住一齊嗌</span></strong> 當係紀念下周同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40065b56f584fdb09daa6e1cbe4ffb7120723624","tid":1699652,"uid":300761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\nbtw垃圾屎維"},{"pid":"ff6d1f3bf8613b6a036f6bb880c0c951751f9cf6","tid":1699652,"uid":62600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"屎維既眼淚好假"},{"pid":"f988c8130835bae9412f4846073bcde8362d57e8","tid":1699652,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"記唔記得女義士失去右眼果晚<br />\n我地係一人一個post咁樣share出去<br />\n最後我地成功咁組織到一個具影響力既行動<br />\n<br />\n今日周同學離開左<br />\n可唔可以用行動表示番<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPzB3qv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPzB3qv.jpg&h=d754a534&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0f4843e47676a498edf2693a2d66aa1c7327893","tid":1699652,"uid":234200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff6d1f3bf8613b6a036f6bb880c0c951751f9cf6","tid":1699652,"uid":62600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"屎維既眼淚好假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass